#
# The following packages provide the minimal set of packages that are
# necessary to create a working system (e.g. networking, zfs rootfs, etc).
#
 * auditd
 * cloud-init
 * debsums
 * grub-pc
 * net-tools
 * open-vm-tools
 * openssh-server
 * ubuntu-minimal
 * zfs-initramfs
 * zfsutils-linux

